name: Inside
description:
- The Meaning -  

Behind your set of eyes; in the deepest parts of your psyche is where you'll find your answer.

A homage to a younger self and the battles that were fought without the understanding that only one's self can hold the "key" for change.


- The Process -

I feed my photography to an AI algorithm which gives me a new image. I take this image and "re-imagine" it; adding my own twists such as symmetry and animation.

I then compose, mix and master a piece of music specifically aimed at capturing the essence of said image.
